articles.title: SWWA_Pressure
articles.contents: This is an example of the reports generated based on the GeoPressureTemplate. You can navigate from this page to all the report generated. Show code # List all the html file found on in the reports/html folder f <- list.files(path = ".", patter = "*.html", recursive = TRUE) f_dirname <- lapply(f, dirname) f_basename <- lapply(f, basename) for (i_f_dir in unique(f_dirname)) { cat(paste("## ", tools::toTitleCase(stringr::str_replace_all(i_f_dir, "_", " ")))) cat("\n") for (i_f in seq_len(length(f))) { if (f_dirname[[i_f]] == i_f_dir) { cat(paste("* ", sub("\\.html$", "", f_basename[[i_f]]), ""), sep = "\n") } } cat("\n") } Basic Trajectory CB594 Technical Details CB594 Wind Trajectory CB594
